body: Urgghhh....I knew it. Shouldn't have looked. Saw Mizone's name tagged in here, knew immediately just scrolling through which was theirs, and now I'm all antsy for someone to translate his new Centaur work. Dammit I'm an idiot. I KNEW I'D WANT IT BUT I LOOKED ANYWAY AGHHHH, HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE THERE'S NO WAY TO KNOOOOOOOOW *cries*
